## 💬 HOW TO WORK AS A TEAM (Sample Dialogue)

Here is an example of how you and your partner should communicate during this round:

> **Field Agent:** "I can see a table called `police_financials`. The columns are `officer_name`, `date`, `amount_inr`, and `sender`."
>
> **Intel Officer:** "What should I query?"
>
> **Field Agent:** "Type: `SELECT * FROM police_financials;` — let's see all the financial records first."
>
> **Intel Officer:** "Done — I see 3 rows. One of them shows a very large amount from a sender called `Offshore_Acc_77492`."
>
> **Field Agent:** "That's suspicious! Now filter by the officer's name — query the officer mentioned in the report."
>
> **Intel Officer:** "Running it now..."

